1
00:00:21,130 --> 00:00:23,710
Mr. Qin Liang, I'm entrusting
my daughter to you.

2
00:00:23,710 --> 00:00:24,800
-Go!
-Minister Shen, don't worry!

3
00:00:24,800 --> 00:00:25,460
Hurry, run!

4
00:00:26,570 --> 00:00:28,320
Must capture Shen Yi's whole family!

5
00:00:28,320 --> 00:00:29,530
Run! Just go!

6
00:00:29,600 --> 00:00:31,390
-Father! Mother!
-Run!

7
00:00:32,430 --> 00:00:33,240
Mother!

8
00:00:33,960 --> 00:00:34,890
Don't be afraid.

9
00:00:35,520 --> 00:00:36,320
Father!

10
00:00:58,200 --> 00:00:59,860
Don't let any of them get away!

11
00:01:09,200 --> 00:01:10,000
Mr. Qin Liang!

12
00:01:28,380 --> 00:01:29,840
My daughter, Wan,

13
00:01:30,380 --> 00:01:31,840
upon reading this letter,

14
00:01:33,070 --> 00:01:34,400
give up seeking justice

15
00:01:34,840 --> 00:01:36,000
and revenge.

16
00:01:36,960 --> 00:01:38,570
Never return to the capital.

17
00:01:39,229 --> 00:01:39,960
Father,

18
00:01:40,590 --> 00:01:42,460
what kind of injustice

19
00:01:42,789 --> 00:01:43,950
could be so severe as to get Mr. Qin Liang

20
00:01:43,950 --> 00:01:45,610
and our entire family killed?

21
00:01:46,430 --> 00:01:48,120
There's no way I'm not

22
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:49,840
avenging your deaths.

23
00:01:50,229 --> 00:01:51,270
From today on,

24
00:01:51,820 --> 00:01:53,090
I am no longer Shen Wan,

25
00:01:53,670 --> 00:01:55,800
but Qin Wan, daughter of Mr. Qin Liang.

26
00:01:56,289 --> 00:01:58,150
I will try to get to the bottom of it

27
00:01:58,590 --> 00:02:00,260
and seek justice for you all.

28
00:03:16,770 --> 00:03:21,410
[Coroner's Diary]

29
00:03:22,079 --> 00:03:25,270
[Episode 1]

30
00:03:53,040 --> 00:03:54,970
Mrs. Huo, what do you mean by this?

31
00:03:55,430 --> 00:03:56,630
Madam Qin,

32
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:59,470
it was a reckless promise we made

33
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:01,680
with your second son's wife

34
00:04:01,700 --> 00:04:02,860
when we were young

35
00:04:03,130 --> 00:04:06,260
[Madam Qin]

36
00:04:03,190 --> 00:04:05,000
to make our children betrothed.

37
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:07,700
Madam Qin, could you please help us

38
00:04:07,090 --> 00:04:09,700
[Mrs. Huo]

39
00:04:07,940 --> 00:04:10,220
cancel this engagement?

40
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:12,300
You're really putting me on the spot.

41
00:04:13,570 --> 00:04:16,570
Although our Qin family hasn't
split into smaller households,

42
00:04:16,570 --> 00:04:18,079
as their stepmother,

43
00:04:18,110 --> 00:04:21,250
how can I interfere in
the second branch's domestic affairs?

44
00:04:21,250 --> 00:04:22,250
That makes sense.

45
00:04:22,510 --> 00:04:24,360
Mrs. Huo, as you know,

46
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:26,600
Qin Liang is not my biological son.

47
00:04:27,170 --> 00:04:28,860
He hasn't been home for years.

48
00:04:29,190 --> 00:04:30,700
His daughter's marriage

49
00:04:31,030 --> 00:04:32,950
is not something I can decide.

50
00:04:34,940 --> 00:04:37,140
But his wife passed away young.

51
00:04:37,170 --> 00:04:40,320
Their daughter has been raised
in Medicine King Valley

52
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:42,280
without parental guidance.

53
00:04:42,430 --> 00:04:43,870
It's been over a decade,

54
00:04:44,390 --> 00:04:47,000
and we don't know
her temperament or character.

55
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:48,730
Mrs. Huo, please rest assured.

56
00:04:48,900 --> 00:04:50,470
When Qin Liang returns,

57
00:04:50,710 --> 00:04:54,070
I will discuss the matter of canceling
the engagement with him.

58
00:04:54,070 --> 00:04:55,790
Our Qin family

59
00:04:55,920 --> 00:04:58,700
won't let a childhood joke

60
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:01,700
ruin the future of our younger generation.

61
00:05:02,960 --> 00:05:03,570
Well...

62
00:05:05,610 --> 00:05:08,210
Grandma, there's something
I need to tell you.

63
00:05:18,580 --> 00:05:19,770
She's back? Why?

64
00:05:25,840 --> 00:05:27,990
Greetings, Grandma.
I'm Qin Wan, your granddaughter.

65
00:05:27,990 --> 00:05:30,850
Greetings, Madam. I'm Fuling.

66
00:05:31,010 --> 00:05:31,920
Mother,

67
00:05:32,280 --> 00:05:35,270
Fuling is the maidservant
who attends to Wan.

68
00:05:32,960 --> 00:05:35,409
[Third Master Qin's Wife, Lin]

69
00:05:35,980 --> 00:05:38,920
I saw her when the second branch
sent New Year's gifts last year.

70
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:40,190
Raise your head.

71
00:05:41,930 --> 00:05:44,450
Are you really Qin Wan?

72
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:46,700
Grandma, I'm Wan.

73
00:05:49,430 --> 00:05:50,860
This is Father's seal.

74
00:05:50,880 --> 00:05:52,300
Please take a look, Grandma.

75
00:05:52,300 --> 00:05:53,110
Caihe.

76
00:06:06,610 --> 00:06:09,010
Of all times to return, you...

77
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:11,480
I encountered a shipwreck
on my way home.

78
00:06:11,500 --> 00:06:13,940
Father saved me at the cost of his life.

79
00:06:13,970 --> 00:06:15,740
Were it not for Father's sacrifice,

80
00:06:15,740 --> 00:06:18,400
I wouldn't have made it here
to see you, Grandma.

81
00:06:18,860 --> 00:06:20,610
This young lady has suffered so much.

82
00:06:20,610 --> 00:06:21,370
Indeed.

83
00:06:23,460 --> 00:06:24,390
Grandma, this is

84
00:06:24,630 --> 00:06:26,890
indeed Uncle Qin Liang's personal seal.

85
00:06:26,960 --> 00:06:29,160
It's only been a few years since he left.

86
00:06:29,350 --> 00:06:31,040
How could he be gone?

87
00:06:33,050 --> 00:06:36,250
Oh, my poor son!

88
00:06:36,280 --> 00:06:37,350
Madam Qin,

89
00:06:37,810 --> 00:06:39,270
since you have
a family affair to handle,

90
00:06:39,270 --> 00:06:40,740
we'll leave you to it.

91
00:06:40,770 --> 00:06:42,740
Let me return
this jade pendant to its owner.

92
00:06:42,740 --> 00:06:44,330
I'll take my leave.

93
00:06:45,540 --> 00:06:46,130
Well...

94
00:06:47,530 --> 00:06:49,080
Quickly, give this jade pendant
back to them.

95
00:06:49,080 --> 00:06:50,920
This engagement cannot be called off.

96
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:51,750
Hurry!

97
00:06:53,159 --> 00:06:55,520
Oh, my poor son!

98
00:06:55,540 --> 00:06:57,600
How could they break off the engagement
in public like this?

99
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:59,659
How disrespectful to our Qin family!

100
00:07:03,790 --> 00:07:05,640
My Lady! My Lady!

101
00:07:05,670 --> 00:07:07,550
Madam, Her Ladyship fainted!

102
00:07:07,570 --> 00:07:08,990
Please go get a physician!

103
00:07:08,990 --> 00:07:11,080
My Lady! My Lady!

104
00:07:23,150 --> 00:07:25,250
My Lady, you freaked me out!

105
00:07:25,360 --> 00:07:27,060
I thought you really fainted.

106
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:30,360
How could we end that dilemma
if I didn't fake passing out?

107
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:31,680
What took you so long?

108
00:07:31,860 --> 00:07:33,120
The moment you fainted,

109
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:35,310
I was soon taken
to face Madam Qin's interrogation.

110
00:07:35,310 --> 00:07:36,390
What did they ask?

111
00:07:38,750 --> 00:07:39,560
Just everything

112
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:41,920
we rehearsed before.

113
00:07:43,380 --> 00:07:44,900
"Madam,

114
00:07:44,930 --> 00:07:46,310
the physician
from Medicine King Valley said

115
00:07:46,310 --> 00:07:48,340
Her Ladyship had fully recovered.

116
00:07:48,370 --> 00:07:51,310
So Master Qin Liang took Her Ladyship
back home for ancestral worship.

117
00:07:51,310 --> 00:07:54,040
But on the way, we encountered a storm.

118
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:55,270
The boat capsized.

119
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:57,390
To save Her Ladyship, Master Qin Liang

120
00:07:57,390 --> 00:07:59,110
was swept away by a wave.

121
00:07:59,510 --> 00:08:01,240
When Her Ladyship came around,

122
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:03,670
Master Qin Liang was already gone.

123
00:08:04,700 --> 00:08:06,170
Her Ladyship had no choice

124
00:08:06,200 --> 00:08:09,190
but to ask someone to help bury
Master Qin Liang properly on the spot.

125
00:08:09,190 --> 00:08:11,670
We made it back, starving and exhausted."

126
00:08:14,840 --> 00:08:18,130
Fortunately, Master Qin Liang
wasn't close to them.

127
00:08:18,150 --> 00:08:20,170
And they haven't seen
his daughter for years.

128
00:08:20,170 --> 00:08:22,500
Or we just couldn't convince them easily.

129
00:08:22,680 --> 00:08:23,600
Good.

130
00:08:24,020 --> 00:08:24,820
Now tell me

131
00:08:24,990 --> 00:08:26,470
about that engagement.

132
00:08:28,700 --> 00:08:32,150
Our master's wife arranged it
with the Huos before she passed away.

133
00:08:32,150 --> 00:08:33,030
Back then,

134
00:08:33,080 --> 00:08:35,150
Mr. Huo was just
a minor county magistrate.

135
00:08:35,150 --> 00:08:37,010
They definitely wanted
to use this childhood betrothal

136
00:08:37,010 --> 00:08:40,030
to build ties with the Qin family's
first branch and the Marquis of Devotion.

137
00:08:40,030 --> 00:08:40,789
Later, Master Qin Liang

138
00:08:40,789 --> 00:08:42,840
took Miss Qin
to Medicine King Valley for treatment.

139
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:43,909
After she passed away last year,

140
00:08:43,909 --> 00:08:45,360
Master Qin Liang was in great agony

141
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:47,160
and didn't inform the Qin family.

142
00:08:47,160 --> 00:08:49,360
Now that Mr. Huo
has been promoted to prefect,

143
00:08:49,360 --> 00:08:51,760
they surely see this engagement
not good enough for them anymore.

144
00:08:51,760 --> 00:08:53,760
What a bunch of treacherous gits.

145
00:08:53,870 --> 00:08:55,270
This is actually better.

146
00:08:55,910 --> 00:08:57,510
Without this engagement,

147
00:08:57,510 --> 00:08:59,720
we can plan better in the future.

148
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:01,960
But the engagement called off in public

149
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:03,360
has disgraced the Qin family.

150
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:05,390
Madam Qin won't dare
to offend Prefect Huo.

151
00:09:05,390 --> 00:09:07,120
She'll surely take it out on me.

152
00:09:07,440 --> 00:09:08,960
You need to be cautious too.

153
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:10,150
Don't worry, My Lady.

154
00:09:10,150 --> 00:09:11,840
I was sold to the Qin family
when I was young.

155
00:09:11,840 --> 00:09:13,970
I'm experienced in dealing with them.

156
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:16,450
Once the remote corner,

157
00:09:16,750 --> 00:09:18,550
now the Buddhist pure land.

158
00:09:19,230 --> 00:09:21,420
Master Pu'an is here.

159
00:09:21,550 --> 00:09:23,720
May all taboos stay away.

160
00:09:24,550 --> 00:09:27,100
Once the remote corner,

161
00:09:27,130 --> 00:09:29,060
now the Buddhist pure land.

162
00:09:29,870 --> 00:09:31,940
Master Pu'an is here...

163
00:09:32,550 --> 00:09:34,760
Looks like Madam Qin thinks
I'm some kind of jinx.

164
00:09:34,760 --> 00:09:36,910
They're holding an exorcism ritual here.

165
00:09:36,910 --> 00:09:37,550
What...

166
00:09:37,570 --> 00:09:39,000
How could she do this?

167
00:09:39,030 --> 00:09:40,600
They're bullying you!

168
00:09:42,660 --> 00:09:43,720
What are you doing?

169
00:09:43,740 --> 00:09:44,760
Madam Qin's order—

170
00:09:44,760 --> 00:09:46,340
Fuling has privately
badmouthed the master

171
00:09:46,340 --> 00:09:48,150
and must be sold
and sent away immediately.

172
00:09:48,150 --> 00:09:49,740
Fuling is my servant.
I will discipline her.

173
00:09:49,740 --> 00:09:51,610
Leave her alone.

174
00:09:51,760 --> 00:09:54,470
You've only been back in the mansion
for a few hours.

175
00:09:54,470 --> 00:09:56,870
And now you already dare
to refute my order?

176
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:59,750
Do you have any respect for your elders?

177
00:10:03,370 --> 00:10:04,370
Please forgive

178
00:10:04,390 --> 00:10:05,650
my rudeness, Grandma.

179
00:10:06,040 --> 00:10:07,730
Fuling accompanied me
on the long journey home.

180
00:10:07,730 --> 00:10:09,380
I'm grateful to her
for not leaving me behind.

181
00:10:09,380 --> 00:10:11,720
Considering her youth
and ignorance, please

182
00:10:11,720 --> 00:10:13,520
forgive her this once, Grandma.

183
00:10:14,320 --> 00:10:15,120
It's my fault.

184
00:10:15,150 --> 00:10:16,440
I dare not speak out of turn again.

185
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:17,770
Please spare me, Madam.

186
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:19,560
Madam,

187
00:10:19,590 --> 00:10:21,050
the ritual has just begun.

188
00:10:21,240 --> 00:10:23,790
Punishing them now would be inauspicious.

189
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:25,800
Why don't we leave it for later?

190
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:27,150
Fine.

191
00:10:28,040 --> 00:10:30,070
Given your merit
in protecting your mistress,

192
00:10:30,070 --> 00:10:32,020
I'll spare you this time.

193
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:34,300
But Wan,

194
00:10:34,420 --> 00:10:36,760
you've been lax
in disciplining your servants.

195
00:10:36,760 --> 00:10:39,790
From today on, you shall
copy scriptures in this courtyard

196
00:10:39,790 --> 00:10:41,340
to pray for your parents

197
00:10:41,670 --> 00:10:43,380
with your monthly allowance
cut for a year.

198
00:10:43,380 --> 00:10:46,380
Only when you learn to be a filial child

199
00:10:46,680 --> 00:10:48,610
can you come out and show your face.

200
00:10:48,670 --> 00:10:50,910
Thank you for showing mercy, Grandma.

201
00:11:04,410 --> 00:11:05,720
It's all my fault.

202
00:11:07,770 --> 00:11:09,830
It's alright. This isn't your fault.

203
00:11:10,030 --> 00:11:11,760
With an intention to punish me,

204
00:11:11,790 --> 00:11:13,920
Madam Qin can easily find ways to do so.

205
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:15,550
Fuling.

206
00:11:16,020 --> 00:11:18,750
Miss Qin was my best friend
in Medicine King Valley.

207
00:11:18,750 --> 00:11:21,150
I, like her, see you as a friend

208
00:11:21,180 --> 00:11:22,440
rather than a servant.

209
00:11:22,750 --> 00:11:25,550
So you don't need to be
a meek servant in front of me.

210
00:11:28,240 --> 00:11:29,150
My Lady...

211
00:11:31,830 --> 00:11:32,610
But

212
00:11:33,100 --> 00:11:34,170
without a monthly allowance,

213
00:11:34,170 --> 00:11:36,630
how are we supposed
to get through this year?

214
00:11:37,150 --> 00:11:37,930
Don't worry.

215
00:11:38,870 --> 00:11:40,000
Even if it's just for

216
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:41,730
her kind and benevolent image,

217
00:11:41,840 --> 00:11:43,300
Madam Qin won't starve us.

218
00:12:00,230 --> 00:12:01,160
Uncle Qin Liang,

219
00:12:01,920 --> 00:12:03,250
you and my parents

220
00:12:03,440 --> 00:12:05,170
all told me not to seek revenge.

221
00:12:05,750 --> 00:12:08,300
But I won't find peace in the world

222
00:12:08,910 --> 00:12:11,640
until the culprit who murdered you
is brought to justice.

223
00:12:11,640 --> 00:12:12,970
Uncle Qin Liang, please

224
00:12:13,210 --> 00:12:15,490
forgive me for using your daughter's name

225
00:12:15,490 --> 00:12:17,150
to carry out dangerous deeds.

226
00:12:18,830 --> 00:12:20,420
Master, please rest assured.

227
00:12:20,420 --> 00:12:21,930
I will definitely follow your words

228
00:12:21,930 --> 00:12:23,650
and take good care of Her Ladyship,

229
00:12:23,650 --> 00:12:24,710
never leaving her.

230
00:12:32,430 --> 00:12:34,720
Your elder brother,
the Marquis of Zhongyong,

231
00:12:33,150 --> 00:12:35,140
[Third Master Qin, Qin An]

232
00:12:34,890 --> 00:12:36,120
is now highly valued

233
00:12:36,350 --> 00:12:38,280
by the Crown Prince in the capital.

234
00:12:38,840 --> 00:12:41,840
Keep in touch with him regularly

235
00:12:42,330 --> 00:12:44,730
and try to secure
an official position for Chen as well.

236
00:12:42,950 --> 00:12:44,580
[Young Master Qin, Qin Chen]

237
00:12:44,760 --> 00:12:47,690
Don't just mess around
in the back courtyard all day.

238
00:12:48,410 --> 00:12:50,560
My elder brother has no time
to pay attention to me.

239
00:12:50,560 --> 00:12:52,160
Although we have the same father,

240
00:12:52,160 --> 00:12:54,640
he's the eldest legitimate son
of Father's first wife,

241
00:12:54,640 --> 00:12:56,400
while I was born to Father's second wife.

242
00:12:56,400 --> 00:12:58,000
We're from different wombs.

243
00:13:05,840 --> 00:13:06,680
Mother!

244
00:13:06,700 --> 00:13:07,910
So what?

245
00:13:07,940 --> 00:13:09,330
Eight taels of silver!

246
00:13:09,350 --> 00:13:11,390
He still has to call me Mother!

247
00:13:14,740 --> 00:13:15,930
This old mansion

248
00:13:16,080 --> 00:13:18,610
still relies on you
to uphold its reputation.

249
00:13:21,530 --> 00:13:23,290
Stop bringing about
"second wife" all the time.

250
00:13:23,290 --> 00:13:25,800
Do you want everyone to know that you
were raised by your father's second wife?

251
00:13:25,800 --> 00:13:27,400
Even your son is grown up now.

252
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:29,790
Why are you still such a failure?

253
00:13:30,910 --> 00:13:33,250
Father, please don't upset Grandma.

254
00:13:33,490 --> 00:13:34,920
Just listen to her.

255
00:13:35,250 --> 00:13:35,950
Go away.

256
00:13:41,090 --> 00:13:43,310
Madam, Miss Qin Wan is here to greet you.

257
00:13:43,710 --> 00:13:44,590
I won't see her.

258
00:13:46,030 --> 00:13:48,600
Madam, today is the day
of the Second Master's funeral.

259
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:50,080
Miss Qin Wan went to pray
early this morning

260
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:51,050
and just returned.

261
00:13:51,050 --> 00:13:52,510
Maybe you should let her in

262
00:13:52,910 --> 00:13:54,580
in case those outsiders

263
00:13:54,600 --> 00:13:57,460
say that you're always biased
toward Master Qin An.

264
00:13:57,670 --> 00:13:58,830
What a nuisance.

265
00:14:01,070 --> 00:14:02,190
Let her wait!

266
00:14:06,600 --> 00:14:07,440
My Lady,

267
00:14:08,440 --> 00:14:10,360
the Madam is talking
with Master Qin An.

268
00:14:10,360 --> 00:14:11,560
Please wait a moment.

269
00:14:11,750 --> 00:14:13,600
I see. Thank you, Miss Caihe.

270
00:14:17,780 --> 00:14:21,240
Prince Jin committed suicide
in the imperial due to his crime.

271
00:14:21,320 --> 00:14:23,340
Didn't they say that
no concrete evidence was found

272
00:14:23,340 --> 00:14:25,070
to prove he killed Consort Jin?

273
00:14:25,360 --> 00:14:27,420
How did he end up committing suicide?

274
00:14:27,440 --> 00:14:28,750
It must be the manipulation

275
00:14:28,750 --> 00:14:30,870
of that Minister S-Shen

276
00:14:30,870 --> 00:14:32,530
of the Supreme Court, Shen Yi.

277
00:14:32,670 --> 00:14:33,990
Mother, I heard that

278
00:14:34,020 --> 00:14:36,040
-My Lady.
-the murder weapon used by Prince Jin

279
00:14:36,040 --> 00:14:37,710
was also hidden by him.

280
00:14:38,840 --> 00:14:41,600
Were it not for his student, Li Muyun,

281
00:14:41,630 --> 00:14:42,940
who reported it to the court,

282
00:14:42,940 --> 00:14:43,890
this case

283
00:14:44,060 --> 00:14:45,520
would have been covered up

284
00:14:45,520 --> 00:14:47,250
by him and Prince Jin together.

285
00:14:47,630 --> 00:14:48,890
Minister Shen

286
00:14:49,230 --> 00:14:51,030
was known as "Shen the Upright,"

287
00:14:51,740 --> 00:14:53,840
a squeaky- clean official,
and an expert in criminal law.

288
00:14:53,840 --> 00:14:55,370
How could he help Prince Jin

289
00:14:55,470 --> 00:14:57,350
do such a corrupt and shady thing?

290
00:14:57,950 --> 00:14:59,150
Was he out of his mind?

291
00:14:59,480 --> 00:15:01,740
You know nothing about the officialdom.

292
00:15:02,360 --> 00:15:03,550
If Shen Yi were truly an upright official,

293
00:15:03,550 --> 00:15:05,410
why would he flee with his family?

294
00:15:05,530 --> 00:15:06,560
I heard that His Majesty

295
00:15:06,560 --> 00:15:08,220
was so irritated
at his fleeing to escape punishment

296
00:15:08,220 --> 00:15:09,560
that His Majesty ordered...

297
00:15:09,560 --> 00:15:12,020
O-Ordered his entire family
to be executed.

298
00:15:12,070 --> 00:15:13,320
But fleeing away didn't help.

299
00:15:13,320 --> 00:15:15,120
It's said that
they encountered a terrible storm

300
00:15:15,120 --> 00:15:16,650
and the entire family died.

301
00:15:17,510 --> 00:15:19,370
"Shen the Upright"? Ridiculous.

302
00:15:19,670 --> 00:15:21,120
Who knows how many shady deals

303
00:15:21,120 --> 00:15:22,580
he made behind the scenes.

304
00:15:23,550 --> 00:15:25,270
This is karma.

305
00:15:25,640 --> 00:15:26,700
He deserved to die.

306
00:15:27,580 --> 00:15:30,440
There's no such thing
as a truly upright official in this world.

307
00:15:30,440 --> 00:15:33,080
Shen Yi merely used his official position

308
00:15:33,790 --> 00:15:37,670
to do some things
to please the common people

309
00:15:37,690 --> 00:15:39,490
and build up his own reputation.

310
00:15:39,700 --> 00:15:42,660
In the end,
he was nothing but a fame-seeker.

311
00:15:42,680 --> 00:15:44,610
Mother, you're absolutely right.

312
00:15:56,610 --> 00:15:59,210
My father would never
collude with Prince Jin.

313
00:15:59,370 --> 00:16:00,560
Who framed him?

314
00:16:01,130 --> 00:16:02,370
Was it Li Muyun

315
00:16:02,710 --> 00:16:03,830
or...

316
00:16:04,630 --> 00:16:06,640
Why did His Majesty
believe those rumors so easily?

317
00:16:06,640 --> 00:16:08,570
Why did Prince Jin commit suicide?

318
00:16:08,740 --> 00:16:09,950
Why?

319
00:16:12,120 --> 00:16:12,960
I'm sorry.

320
00:16:14,630 --> 00:16:15,430
No.

321
00:16:15,960 --> 00:16:17,290
I must go to the capital.

322
00:16:17,600 --> 00:16:19,660
I must go to the capital immediately.

323
00:16:21,520 --> 00:16:22,760
Madam, are you tired?

324
00:16:22,780 --> 00:16:24,410
I'll have someone
send us back to the mansion.

325
00:16:24,410 --> 00:16:26,800
I can seldom be this free and at ease.

326
00:16:26,970 --> 00:16:28,970
If the Marquis finds out about this,

327
00:16:29,230 --> 00:16:31,410
I won't be able to sneak out again
in the future.

328
00:16:31,410 --> 00:16:32,400
Back in the day,

329
00:16:33,270 --> 00:16:36,600
I accompanied the Old Marquis
on the military campaigns...

330
00:16:36,950 --> 00:16:39,220
Madam! Madam!

331
00:16:40,310 --> 00:16:41,550
What's wrong, Madam?

332
00:16:42,760 --> 00:16:44,040
Madam, wake up!

333
00:16:44,570 --> 00:16:45,360
Young lady,

334
00:16:45,390 --> 00:16:47,120
could you fetch us a physician?

335
00:16:47,120 --> 00:16:47,840
Madam!

336
00:16:47,840 --> 00:16:48,870
Miss, you'd better

337
00:16:48,870 --> 00:16:50,360
send someone to inform
your family of this.

338
00:16:50,360 --> 00:16:51,440
Madam!

339
00:16:54,150 --> 00:16:54,790
No way.

340
00:16:54,960 --> 00:16:56,890
My madam was fine just a moment ago.

341
00:16:56,990 --> 00:16:58,790
Please go get a physician for us.

342
00:16:59,630 --> 00:17:00,080
Madam.

343
00:17:00,080 --> 00:17:01,440
Lay the madam down flat.

344
00:17:01,720 --> 00:17:02,550
Hurry.

345
00:17:03,570 --> 00:17:05,390
Your madam has
an old ailment of wind evil.

346
00:17:05,390 --> 00:17:07,210
Her symptoms worsened six months ago.

347
00:17:07,210 --> 00:17:08,650
Just now, her body
became rigid and unresponsive,

348
00:17:08,650 --> 00:17:10,770
her tongue stiff, throat obstructed,
pulse sluggish, and qi stagnant.

349
00:17:10,770 --> 00:17:12,579
It's a case of wind hysteria
due to wind evil entering the liver.

350
00:17:12,579 --> 00:17:13,640
Yes, you're right.

351
00:17:14,869 --> 00:17:16,200
Remember my technique.

352
00:17:26,030 --> 00:17:27,760
Bring me paper and an ink brush.

353
00:17:29,720 --> 00:17:30,920
Continue massaging.

354
00:17:33,050 --> 00:17:34,470
Based on my prescription,

355
00:17:34,470 --> 00:17:37,150
decoct and feed the medicine
to her within two hours.

356
00:17:37,150 --> 00:17:39,030
Keep massaging according to my technique.

357
00:17:39,030 --> 00:17:40,300
Acupuncture would work best for her

358
00:17:40,300 --> 00:17:41,890
if there's someone skilled in it.

359
00:17:41,890 --> 00:17:44,440
If she can break into
a heavy sweat before nightfall,

360
00:17:44,440 --> 00:17:46,040
she'll get over this crisis.

361
00:17:46,240 --> 00:17:46,920
If not,

362
00:17:47,430 --> 00:17:50,360
you gotta prepare for her funeral
within seven days.

363
00:17:51,720 --> 00:17:52,820
Thank you.

364
00:18:11,110 --> 00:18:12,750
My Lady, where have you been?

365
00:18:13,480 --> 00:18:14,400
I told Caihe that

366
00:18:14,400 --> 00:18:16,350
you lost your purse
and went to look for it.

367
00:18:16,350 --> 00:18:17,960
You didn't go
greet Madam Qin this morning.

368
00:18:17,960 --> 00:18:18,820
She was furious

369
00:18:18,820 --> 00:18:20,400
and confined you to quarters again.

370
00:18:20,400 --> 00:18:21,200
Fuling,

371
00:18:21,530 --> 00:18:22,640
I am Shen Wan,

372
00:18:22,690 --> 00:18:23,580
not Qin Wan.

373
00:18:31,040 --> 00:18:33,920
My Lady, you mustn't say
such things recklessly again.

374
00:18:33,920 --> 00:18:35,580
My father neither
colluded with Prince Jin

375
00:18:35,580 --> 00:18:37,240
nor did he flee out of fear of punishment.

376
00:18:37,240 --> 00:18:38,800
He and my mother were set up
and killed by someone.

377
00:18:38,800 --> 00:18:40,100
I saw it with my own eyes.

378
00:18:40,100 --> 00:18:41,030
I also know that

379
00:18:41,290 --> 00:18:42,240
Lord Shen

380
00:18:42,260 --> 00:18:44,870
is an absolutely upright
and good official.

381
00:18:45,350 --> 00:18:47,240
All those who have
slandered and framed him

382
00:18:47,240 --> 00:18:48,830
will be hit hard by karma.

383
00:18:50,020 --> 00:18:51,420
I want to go to the capital

384
00:18:51,790 --> 00:18:53,590
to find my parents' bodies

385
00:18:53,810 --> 00:18:55,980
and clear their names
of false accusations.

386
00:18:55,980 --> 00:18:58,140
Okay, I'm going to beg Madam Qin

387
00:18:58,170 --> 00:18:59,690
to let us go to the capital.

388
00:19:01,920 --> 00:19:03,500
She won't let us leave.

389
00:19:03,990 --> 00:19:05,590
I'll figure out a way myself.

390
00:19:06,380 --> 00:19:08,310
But I can't take you to the capital.

391
00:19:10,410 --> 00:19:12,310
The case of my father and Prince Jin

392
00:19:12,310 --> 00:19:13,890
concerns His Majesty's will.

393
00:19:13,890 --> 00:19:16,020
It's more treacherous than I thought.

394
00:19:16,270 --> 00:19:18,000
It's safer for you to stay here.

395
00:19:19,740 --> 00:19:21,960
Wan, the first day I got
to the Medicine King Valley,

396
00:19:21,960 --> 00:19:24,890
you taught me
how to take care of Miss Qin step by step.

397
00:19:24,890 --> 00:19:26,620
After Miss Qin passed away,

398
00:19:26,810 --> 00:19:28,570
you kept me by your side.

399
00:19:28,920 --> 00:19:31,240
I know I'm not much help

400
00:19:31,290 --> 00:19:32,860
when it comes to big things,

401
00:19:33,760 --> 00:19:35,110
but I can keep you company

402
00:19:35,110 --> 00:19:36,500
and take care of you!

403
00:19:36,880 --> 00:19:39,110
And I swore
before Master Qin Liang's grave that

404
00:19:39,110 --> 00:19:41,150
I would never leave you in this lifetime.

405
00:19:41,150 --> 00:19:42,750
If you don't take me with you,

406
00:19:42,990 --> 00:19:44,160
I'll go on my own

407
00:19:44,180 --> 00:19:45,900
to find you in the capital!

408
00:19:47,880 --> 00:19:48,670
Get up.

409
00:19:53,720 --> 00:19:56,610
Didn't we say no more tears?

410
00:19:59,400 --> 00:20:00,440
I promise you.

411
00:20:01,030 --> 00:20:02,230
We will never be apart

412
00:20:02,250 --> 00:20:03,690
in this lifetime.

413
00:20:23,660 --> 00:20:26,930
Grandma, these fabrics are nice,

414
00:20:27,570 --> 00:20:30,080
but they still can't compare
to that gold-speckled red gauze

415
00:20:29,010 --> 00:20:31,480
[Fifth Lady, Qin Xiang]

416
00:20:30,260 --> 00:20:31,880
from your storeroom.

417
00:20:31,960 --> 00:20:33,360
You've got quite the eye.

418
00:20:33,430 --> 00:20:35,760
That was a gift from the Emperor

419
00:20:36,110 --> 00:20:37,440
to the Marquis of Devotion
and our third branch of the Qin family.

420
00:20:37,440 --> 00:20:39,500
There were only three bolts in total.

421
00:20:39,500 --> 00:20:41,960
How could you possibly get
to use one of them?

422
00:20:48,160 --> 00:20:50,710
Grandma, the Marquis of Anyang's Mansion

423
00:20:50,730 --> 00:20:53,160
is the most prestigious family
in all of Jingzhou.

424
00:20:53,160 --> 00:20:55,560
It's a rare honor that we were
even invited to this wedding.

425
00:20:55,560 --> 00:20:57,160
If I dress well,

426
00:20:57,180 --> 00:20:59,290
won't it reflect glory

427
00:20:59,320 --> 00:21:00,850
on the Qin family as a whole?

428
00:21:01,680 --> 00:21:03,960
Oh, I see your little plan.

429
00:21:05,200 --> 00:21:06,070
Fine.

430
00:21:06,350 --> 00:21:09,310
Have your mother sew two
beautiful dresses.

431
00:21:09,850 --> 00:21:11,440
You'd better wear them properly.

432
00:21:11,440 --> 00:21:12,830
Don't go ruining them.

433
00:21:14,030 --> 00:21:15,640
If you can catch the eye

434
00:21:15,750 --> 00:21:17,830
of Grand Princess,

435
00:21:18,680 --> 00:21:20,430
a good marriage

436
00:21:20,800 --> 00:21:22,920
will naturally come knocking.

437
00:21:24,160 --> 00:21:26,820
Xiang, what are you waiting for?
Thank Grandma.

438
00:21:27,310 --> 00:21:28,960
Thank you, Grandma.

439
00:21:29,320 --> 00:21:31,050
Grandma, you treat me the best!

440
00:21:31,880 --> 00:21:33,600
-I know you.
-Madam.

441
00:21:35,320 --> 00:21:38,470
Princess Yongning
of the Marquis of Anyang's Mansion
has come to vist.

442
00:21:38,470 --> 00:21:39,800
Quickly, invite her in!

443
00:21:50,560 --> 00:21:52,370
[Princess Yongning, Yue Ning]

444
00:21:52,950 --> 00:21:55,840
Greetings, Princess Yongning.

445
00:21:56,650 --> 00:21:57,780
Please rise, Madam.

446
00:21:57,960 --> 00:21:59,450
There's no need for formalities.

447
00:21:59,450 --> 00:22:00,570
Please have a seat, Madam.

448
00:22:00,570 --> 00:22:01,900
Please, Your Ladyship.

449
00:22:21,120 --> 00:22:23,560
Your Ladyship, may I ask what brings

450
00:22:23,580 --> 00:22:25,620
you to our humble home today?

451
00:22:26,310 --> 00:22:26,970
Lvxiu.

452
00:22:30,910 --> 00:22:32,810
I'm here on behalf of Grand Princess

453
00:22:32,810 --> 00:22:36,070
to express gratitude for
Miss Qin's lifesaving kindness.

454
00:22:37,370 --> 00:22:38,610
You mean Wan?

455
00:22:40,030 --> 00:22:41,510
-Let me help you.
-No need.

456
00:22:41,510 --> 00:22:42,530
Let me do it myself.

457
00:22:42,530 --> 00:22:43,330
Give me one.

458
00:22:43,360 --> 00:22:44,280
Miss Qin!

459
00:22:45,570 --> 00:22:46,380
Miss Qin!

460
00:22:46,690 --> 00:22:47,410
Hurry up!

461
00:22:47,440 --> 00:22:48,920
Change your robes and go to the main hall!

462
00:22:48,920 --> 00:22:50,790
The Princess Yongning from
Marquis of Anyang's Mansion

463
00:22:50,790 --> 00:22:53,590
has come to thank you in
person for saving her life!

464
00:22:53,590 --> 00:22:55,160
Princess Yongning?

465
00:22:55,790 --> 00:22:57,450
I haven't saved any princess.

466
00:22:57,640 --> 00:22:59,590
Did you aid an elderly madam

467
00:22:59,590 --> 00:23:00,850
on the street days ago?

468
00:23:01,280 --> 00:23:02,310
That elderly madam

469
00:23:02,310 --> 00:23:03,950
was none other than the Grand Princess,

470
00:23:03,950 --> 00:23:05,750
the matriarch of the
Marquis of Anyang's Mansion!

471
00:23:05,750 --> 00:23:08,590
Princess Yongning is Grand Princess' own
granddaughter,

472
00:23:08,590 --> 00:23:11,720
She's come in person to
convey her grandma's gratitude.

473
00:23:12,090 --> 00:23:13,430
You two, stop what you're doing.

474
00:23:13,430 --> 00:23:15,100
Come help Miss Qin with these buckets!

475
00:23:15,100 --> 00:23:15,930
-Yes.
-Hurry.

476
00:23:18,390 --> 00:23:20,310
Please go ahead, Miss Caihe.

477
00:23:20,920 --> 00:23:22,180
I'll be there shortly.

478
00:23:22,210 --> 00:23:22,820
Yes.

479
00:23:28,550 --> 00:23:29,350
My Lady,

480
00:23:29,550 --> 00:23:31,310
the person you saved is the
Grand Princess—

481
00:23:31,310 --> 00:23:33,070
His Majesty's own aunt!

482
00:23:33,370 --> 00:23:35,480
I only thought she looked wealthy.

483
00:23:35,890 --> 00:23:36,790
I had no idea

484
00:23:36,960 --> 00:23:38,420
her status was so exalted.

485
00:23:38,560 --> 00:23:39,450
Well then, this means

486
00:23:39,450 --> 00:23:41,710
we might finally return to the
capital soon.

487
00:23:41,710 --> 00:23:43,710
Then hurry and change your clothes!

488
00:23:46,810 --> 00:23:47,520
No, I won't.

489
00:23:47,920 --> 00:23:49,650
I'll go dressed just like this.

490
00:23:50,190 --> 00:23:52,390
I want Princess Yongning to see exactly

491
00:23:52,570 --> 00:23:53,740
how I've been living

492
00:23:53,870 --> 00:23:55,330
in the Qin family.

493
00:24:11,390 --> 00:24:13,800
Greetings, Grandma.

494
00:24:14,820 --> 00:24:16,130
She dresses so plainly.

495
00:24:16,130 --> 00:24:17,990
What a disgrace to the Qin family.

496
00:24:20,440 --> 00:24:24,400
Wan, why are you so late?

497
00:24:26,200 --> 00:24:29,830
Hurry and pay your respects
to Princess Yongning.

498
00:24:33,330 --> 00:24:34,730
No need for formalities.

499
00:24:34,840 --> 00:24:36,690
Miss Qin, do you remember her?

500
00:24:37,640 --> 00:24:38,270
It's you?

501
00:24:38,750 --> 00:24:40,470
How is your family's madam?

502
00:24:40,650 --> 00:24:42,400
Thanks to your timely treatment,

503
00:24:42,400 --> 00:24:44,010
Grand Princess is feeling much better.

504
00:24:44,010 --> 00:24:46,740
I've come on her behalf to
express our gratitude.

505
00:24:48,160 --> 00:24:50,090
What does she know about medicine?

506
00:24:50,110 --> 00:24:52,070
It was pure luck, nothing more.

507
00:24:53,170 --> 00:24:54,170
Wan,

508
00:24:54,200 --> 00:24:56,440
you never mentioned

509
00:24:56,460 --> 00:24:58,520
what happened that day after you returned.

510
00:24:58,520 --> 00:24:59,330
See?

511
00:24:59,700 --> 00:25:03,150
Miss Lvxiu has been looking
all over for you.

512
00:25:04,550 --> 00:25:07,030
As long as the right person
was found, it's fine.

513
00:25:07,030 --> 00:25:08,690
Miss Qin, come with me.

514
00:25:08,940 --> 00:25:12,400
My grandma is still waiting
for your follow-up consultation.

515
00:25:14,700 --> 00:25:17,700
Since the Princess has come
to invite you personally,

516
00:25:18,540 --> 00:25:22,100
you must serve the Grand Princess well.

517
00:25:22,770 --> 00:25:25,850
Don't be reckless and cause trouble.

518
00:25:29,370 --> 00:25:30,220
Your Ladyship,

519
00:25:30,220 --> 00:25:32,960
may I also go and pay my
respects to the Grand Princess?

520
00:25:32,960 --> 00:25:34,140
What are you going there for?

521
00:25:34,140 --> 00:25:35,570
My grandma doesn't even know you.

522
00:25:35,570 --> 00:25:36,250
I...

523
00:25:42,160 --> 00:25:43,610
Miss Qin, please.

524
00:25:54,990 --> 00:25:55,920
Mother.

525
00:25:56,310 --> 00:25:57,370
Alright, alright.

526
00:26:10,640 --> 00:26:12,310
Your Ladyship, what are you looking at?

527
00:26:12,310 --> 00:26:13,310
You're so young.

528
00:26:13,710 --> 00:26:16,510
I've never seen such a
youthful divine physician.

529
00:26:16,550 --> 00:26:19,050
Skill in medicine lies in talent
and experience,

530
00:26:19,050 --> 00:26:20,440
not age.

531
00:26:21,030 --> 00:26:21,920
Moreover,

532
00:26:22,160 --> 00:26:24,040
I grew up in Medicine King Valley,

533
00:26:24,180 --> 00:26:25,370
and trained in both medicine
and alchemy from childhood.

534
00:26:25,370 --> 00:26:26,850
Naturally, my understanding
is a little different.

535
00:26:26,850 --> 00:26:27,810
So

536
00:26:27,840 --> 00:26:29,360
you're a medical talent?

537
00:26:29,890 --> 00:26:30,720
Perfect!

538
00:26:30,740 --> 00:26:32,460
I'm a martial arts talent!

539
00:26:33,010 --> 00:26:34,140
My father said that

