00:26:34,170 --> 00:26:35,410
if I'd been born a boy,

541
00:26:35,430 --> 00:26:37,360
I'd have outshone all my brothers.

542
00:26:37,670 --> 00:26:39,970
My father often regrets that I
was born a girl.

543
00:26:39,970 --> 00:26:40,970
Otherwise,

544
00:26:41,180 --> 00:26:43,310
I would surely be a pillar of the state.

545
00:26:45,430 --> 00:26:46,510
So it's a case of

546
00:26:46,530 --> 00:26:48,340
talent recognizing talent.

547
00:26:48,740 --> 00:26:50,670
I've finally met a kindred spirit.

548
00:26:51,990 --> 00:26:53,390
You haven't paid yet.

549
00:26:53,410 --> 00:26:54,520
Officer!

550
00:26:54,550 --> 00:26:56,150
-You can't take it!
-Go away!

551
00:26:56,640 --> 00:26:58,030
How can this soldier bully
people like this?

552
00:26:58,030 --> 00:26:58,830
Officer!

553
00:26:58,830 --> 00:27:00,830
There are elderly at home
waiting for money to buy medicine.

554
00:27:00,830 --> 00:27:01,880
Officer!

555
00:27:01,880 --> 00:27:03,860
What's wrong with me taking
a few of your chickens?

556
00:27:03,860 --> 00:27:05,480
You just look like you need a beating.

557
00:27:05,480 --> 00:27:06,080
Get away!

558
00:27:06,610 --> 00:27:07,480
Let go! You...

559
00:27:07,750 --> 00:27:08,440
Officer!

560
00:27:09,210 --> 00:27:11,140
Your Ladyship, come down quickly!

561
00:27:16,850 --> 00:27:18,450
The Shuoxi Army has arrived.

562
00:27:35,290 --> 00:27:36,610
These soldiers

563
00:27:36,720 --> 00:27:38,240
look battle-hardened.

564
00:27:38,500 --> 00:27:40,150
Their fierce aura

565
00:27:40,170 --> 00:27:41,990
sets them apart from the
provincial troops.

566
00:27:41,990 --> 00:27:44,320
They serve under the Black
Armor Guards,
Young Marshal of Shuoxi Army.

567
00:27:44,320 --> 00:27:46,350
The Young Marshal has
fought bloodily across Shuoxi.

568
00:27:46,350 --> 00:27:47,850
His name strikes fear in enemy ranks,

569
00:27:47,850 --> 00:27:49,650
and his forces are unstoppable.

570
00:27:54,220 --> 00:27:55,030
Stop!

571
00:27:56,520 --> 00:27:57,330
Who are you?

572
00:27:57,570 --> 00:27:59,500
According to Shuoxi military law,

573
00:27:59,640 --> 00:28:01,590
anyone who oppresses the people

574
00:28:01,840 --> 00:28:03,500
shall be executed on the spot.

575
00:28:03,630 --> 00:28:05,960
Anyone caught stealing for personal gain

576
00:28:05,970 --> 00:28:07,900
shall be executed on the spot.

577
00:28:08,380 --> 00:28:09,250
Executed?

578
00:28:09,750 --> 00:28:10,790
What do your Shuoxi military laws

579
00:28:10,790 --> 00:28:12,070
have to do with us Jingzhou soldiers?

580
00:28:12,070 --> 00:28:13,640
Anyone who defies our superiors

581
00:28:13,640 --> 00:28:14,770
and disobeys orders

582
00:28:15,200 --> 00:28:16,260
shall be executed!

583
00:28:16,350 --> 00:28:17,150
How dare you!

584
00:28:23,640 --> 00:28:25,840
He deserves it for bullying civilians.

585
00:28:27,370 --> 00:28:29,640
Send his body to the garrison commander,

586
00:28:29,990 --> 00:28:30,910
and tell him

587
00:28:30,930 --> 00:28:32,660
if he can't control his troops,

588
00:28:32,680 --> 00:28:34,470
I, Yan Chi, will take over for him.

589
00:28:34,470 --> 00:28:35,270
Yes!

590
00:28:42,460 --> 00:28:43,260
Officer.

591
00:28:48,230 --> 00:28:49,790
Thank you, Officer.

592
00:28:49,810 --> 00:28:52,070
That's the Young Marshal of Shuoxi Army,

593
00:28:52,070 --> 00:28:53,110
my cousin,

594
00:28:53,400 --> 00:28:55,630
the legendary God of War, Yan Chi!

595
00:28:55,940 --> 00:28:57,160
He joined the army at 10,

596
00:28:57,160 --> 00:28:58,990
and by 15, he was earning
top honors every year.

597
00:28:58,990 --> 00:29:00,520
Pretty impressive, right?

598
00:29:01,420 --> 00:29:02,390
Indeed.

599
00:29:03,440 --> 00:29:04,110
Thank you, Officer.

600
00:29:04,110 --> 00:29:05,240
Thank you, Officer.

601
00:29:20,480 --> 00:29:23,490
[Marquis of Anyang's Mansion]

602
00:29:30,030 --> 00:29:32,950
[Grand Princess]

603
00:29:37,460 --> 00:29:39,390
Madam.

604
00:29:39,410 --> 00:29:41,140
The Crown Prince has returned!

605
00:29:42,370 --> 00:29:43,100
Great Aunt,

606
00:29:43,770 --> 00:29:45,370
I've come to pay my respects.

607
00:29:52,770 --> 00:29:55,630
You old rascal! Still as playful
as ever at your age?

608
00:29:57,700 --> 00:29:58,510
Come here.

609
00:29:59,110 --> 00:30:02,160
The Shuoxi Army has
heavy duties at the border.

610
00:30:02,510 --> 00:30:03,710
How could your father

611
00:30:03,810 --> 00:30:06,000
possibly let you wander off?

612
00:30:06,020 --> 00:30:08,790
Guess, Great Aunt.

613
00:30:09,410 --> 00:30:11,450
You snuck out on your own,

614
00:30:11,480 --> 00:30:12,140
didn't you?

615
00:30:13,430 --> 00:30:15,360
I can never hide anything from you.

616
00:30:15,640 --> 00:30:16,880
I had some disagreements with my father

617
00:30:16,880 --> 00:30:18,610
over military affairs.

618
00:30:18,880 --> 00:30:20,600
I ran back in a fit of anger.

619
00:30:21,170 --> 00:30:22,900
Did he strike you again?

620
00:30:25,150 --> 00:30:27,390
Why can't he ever

621
00:30:27,410 --> 00:30:29,000
grasp a father's kindness?

622
00:30:29,350 --> 00:30:30,350
I'm used to it.

623
00:30:30,570 --> 00:30:33,290
It's only because your mother
passed too soon,

624
00:30:33,400 --> 00:30:34,880
and you're his only son left

625
00:30:34,880 --> 00:30:36,620
to keep him company.

626
00:30:37,030 --> 00:30:39,780
Just cut him some slack.

627
00:30:40,550 --> 00:30:41,780
He's been lonely most of his life.

628
00:30:41,780 --> 00:30:43,510
He doesn't need me to back down.

629
00:30:44,060 --> 00:30:45,060
In his heart,

630
00:30:45,880 --> 00:30:47,210
I'm probably not even half as important

631
00:30:47,210 --> 00:30:48,650
as the Shuoxi Army.

632
00:30:49,070 --> 00:30:49,940
Chi.

633
00:30:51,240 --> 00:30:52,370
It's been years.

634
00:30:52,400 --> 00:30:54,140
You're looking more impressive than ever.

635
00:30:54,140 --> 00:30:56,300
You were so decisive

636
00:30:56,400 --> 00:30:57,640
and commanding
in the marketplace.

637
00:30:57,640 --> 00:30:58,290
Grandma.

638
00:30:58,320 --> 00:30:59,850
Gap Tooth has grown so tall.

639
00:31:00,070 --> 00:31:02,070
Let me check if your teeth are all in.

640
00:31:02,370 --> 00:31:03,600
Don't call me Gap Tooth.

641
00:31:03,600 --> 00:31:05,860
My teeth have all grown in
for a long time!

642
00:31:12,400 --> 00:31:13,050
Come.

643
00:31:26,930 --> 00:31:29,100
Chi, why are you distracted?

644
00:31:29,130 --> 00:31:30,590
Are you looking down on me?

645
00:31:32,640 --> 00:31:34,370
This lady looks familiar to me.

646
00:31:35,840 --> 00:31:37,250
This is Miss Qin of the Qin family.

647
00:31:37,250 --> 00:31:38,380
How do you know her?

648
00:31:42,320 --> 00:31:45,050
I, Qin Wan, pay my respects
to the Grand Princess.

649
00:31:46,050 --> 00:31:48,810
So you're Miss Qin of the Qin family?

650
00:31:50,120 --> 00:31:50,920
Come here.

651
00:31:52,160 --> 00:31:53,420
Little Medical Fairy,

652
00:31:54,030 --> 00:31:55,480
stay away from those two.

653
00:31:55,640 --> 00:31:57,310
Don't let them hurt you.

654
00:31:58,650 --> 00:32:00,450
A few days ago on the street,

655
00:32:00,480 --> 00:32:02,000
I had a relapse of my old ailment.

656
00:32:02,000 --> 00:32:04,040
Luckily, you treated me.

657
00:32:04,400 --> 00:32:05,820
Otherwise, Chi

658
00:32:05,960 --> 00:32:08,490
wouldn't have been able to
see his great aunt.

659
00:32:08,780 --> 00:32:10,550
You saved someone on the street.

660
00:32:10,550 --> 00:32:11,740
Miss Qin, may I ask

661
00:32:11,960 --> 00:32:13,690
where you learned your skills?

662
00:32:14,270 --> 00:32:16,330
I grew up in the Medicine King Valley;

663
00:32:16,360 --> 00:32:18,800
all the doctors and patients there
are my teachers.

664
00:32:18,800 --> 00:32:22,260
So that's why Great Aunt
calls you the "Little Medical Fairy?"

665
00:32:22,670 --> 00:32:23,470
Chi,

666
00:32:24,290 --> 00:32:25,530
how long will you stay

667
00:32:25,970 --> 00:32:27,490
in Jingzhou this time?

668
00:32:27,590 --> 00:32:28,830
Don't worry, Great Aunt.

669
00:32:28,830 --> 00:32:30,030
I definitely want to celebrate

670
00:32:30,030 --> 00:32:31,960
my cousin Jia's wedding properly.

671
00:32:32,160 --> 00:32:33,290
That's more like it.

672
00:32:33,680 --> 00:32:34,820
By the way, Little Medical Fairy,

673
00:32:34,820 --> 00:32:36,380
you must come to

674
00:32:36,410 --> 00:32:38,020
my eldest grandson's wedding.

675
00:32:38,020 --> 00:32:39,420
I'll send you an invitation.

676
00:32:39,420 --> 00:32:40,950
Thank you, Grand Princess.

677
00:32:41,110 --> 00:32:41,880
However,

678
00:32:42,230 --> 00:32:43,750
it hasn't been three years
since my father's funeral.

679
00:32:43,750 --> 00:32:45,040
We're a family of generals.

680
00:32:45,040 --> 00:32:46,230
We don't fuss over such things.

681
00:32:46,230 --> 00:32:47,160
Just consider it

682
00:32:47,250 --> 00:32:48,730
as you coming to keep me
company and have a chat.

683
00:32:48,730 --> 00:32:50,640
We'll close the door

684
00:32:50,700 --> 00:32:52,360
and have our own little feast.

685
00:32:52,750 --> 00:32:54,610
Alright, I'll do as you say.

686
00:32:54,810 --> 00:32:56,980
But today, you must listen to me as well.

687
00:32:56,980 --> 00:32:58,080
It's getting late.

688
00:32:58,150 --> 00:33:00,680
I should take your pulse
and apply some acupuncture.

689
00:33:00,680 --> 00:33:01,210
Alright.

690
00:33:01,650 --> 00:33:03,780
Then I'll go out and practice with Chi.

691
00:33:04,580 --> 00:33:06,700
I still need to keep Great Aunt company.

692
00:33:06,700 --> 00:33:07,720
No distractions allowed

693
00:33:07,720 --> 00:33:09,410
during treatment.

694
00:33:09,850 --> 00:33:11,380
Did you hear that? Let's go.

695
00:33:15,070 --> 00:33:16,970
[Grace and Purity]

696
00:33:16,360 --> 00:33:17,160
My Lady!

697
00:33:17,990 --> 00:33:19,080
My Lady, look,

698
00:33:19,100 --> 00:33:20,450
I got new clothes!

699
00:33:21,440 --> 00:33:22,070
This is great.

700
00:33:22,070 --> 00:33:23,880
No more patchwork for me!

701
00:33:26,860 --> 00:33:28,970
This house is huge!

702
00:33:32,490 --> 00:33:35,100
My Lady, why aren't you happy?

703
00:33:35,480 --> 00:33:37,830
Tinglan Garden is the best
courtyard in the Qin Mansion.

704
00:33:37,830 --> 00:33:39,240
Now it's ours.

705
00:33:39,240 --> 00:33:40,600
It feels like a dream!

706
00:33:41,000 --> 00:33:42,870
These were never mine to begin with.

707
00:33:42,870 --> 00:33:44,600
What's there to be happy about?

708
00:33:47,960 --> 00:33:49,110
Wan!

709
00:33:52,030 --> 00:33:53,510
-Wan!
-Third Madam.

710
00:33:54,880 --> 00:33:56,070
Miss Qin.

711
00:33:56,350 --> 00:33:58,140
Wan, how is it?

712
00:33:58,270 --> 00:34:00,780
Is this courtyard to your liking?

713
00:34:01,700 --> 00:34:03,030
Thank you, Third Madam.

714
00:34:03,440 --> 00:34:04,300
Call me Auntie.

715
00:34:05,160 --> 00:34:05,750
Auntie.

716
00:34:09,000 --> 00:34:11,770
Look at our Wan—

717
00:34:12,570 --> 00:34:14,139
such a sweet voice,

718
00:34:14,770 --> 00:34:16,770
that face, that figure—

719
00:34:16,790 --> 00:34:18,630
truly the best in Jingzhou.

720
00:34:19,590 --> 00:34:22,679
No wonder
the Grand Princess favors you so much.

721
00:34:22,780 --> 00:34:24,330
I've been so busy

722
00:34:24,510 --> 00:34:27,219
this past year,

723
00:34:27,449 --> 00:34:30,010
so I've forgotten to bring you

724
00:34:30,040 --> 00:34:31,440
these things I prepared.

725
00:34:31,670 --> 00:34:33,670
Take a look; do you like them?

726
00:34:36,080 --> 00:34:37,320
I don't need so many.

727
00:34:37,429 --> 00:34:38,139
Keep them.

728
00:34:38,469 --> 00:34:40,270
You can alternate between them.

729
00:34:40,280 --> 00:34:42,070
When you're all dressed up tomorrow,

730
00:34:42,070 --> 00:34:44,330
it'll make the Grand Princess happy too.

731
00:34:45,389 --> 00:34:46,449
Thank you, Auntie.

732
00:34:46,800 --> 00:34:48,949
We're family; no need to be so formal.

733
00:34:48,980 --> 00:34:49,790
Alright.

734
00:34:49,810 --> 00:34:52,000
I won't disturb your studies anymore.

735
00:34:52,480 --> 00:34:53,320
Here.

736
00:34:53,320 --> 00:34:54,360
All of you, follow me.

737
00:34:54,360 --> 00:34:55,800
Put all these over there.

738
00:34:56,179 --> 00:34:57,180
Put them all here.

739
00:34:57,990 --> 00:34:59,850
Yes, yes, quickly put them there.

740
00:35:02,430 --> 00:35:04,630
Such a good girl.

741
00:35:11,000 --> 00:35:12,470
[Marquis of Anyang's Mansion]

742
00:35:19,230 --> 00:35:20,760
Greetings, Your Highness.

743
00:35:25,880 --> 00:35:27,210
Greetings, Great Aunt.

744
00:35:29,130 --> 00:35:31,050
Greetings, Your Highness.

745
00:35:31,710 --> 00:35:32,880
Chi,

746
00:35:33,230 --> 00:35:34,550
what are you doing here

747
00:35:34,550 --> 00:35:36,080
instead of sitting in the front hall?

748
00:35:36,080 --> 00:35:36,750
Look,

749
00:35:37,070 --> 00:35:39,340
you're making Wan nervous.

750
00:35:39,880 --> 00:35:42,140
Miss Qin, this is our first meeting,

751
00:35:43,150 --> 00:35:43,960
but why does it

752
00:35:44,230 --> 00:35:46,030
seem like you're a bit

753
00:35:46,350 --> 00:35:46,950
wary of me?

754
00:35:50,420 --> 00:35:51,730
Your Highness, just a few days ago

755
00:35:51,730 --> 00:35:53,670
I saw you display great martial skill

756
00:35:53,670 --> 00:35:54,880
and strict discipline.

757
00:35:54,880 --> 00:35:56,480
Naturally, I hold you in awe.

758
00:35:58,000 --> 00:35:59,860
The fierceness of the Shuoxi Army

759
00:36:00,050 --> 00:36:01,510
is reserved for the enemy.

760
00:36:01,880 --> 00:36:03,410
We never harm the innocent.

761
00:36:04,190 --> 00:36:06,260
Thanks to the Shuoxi Army for

762
00:36:06,720 --> 00:36:10,320
defending the nation and
bringing peace to countless families.

763
00:36:11,780 --> 00:36:13,450
Alright, alright.

764
00:36:13,520 --> 00:36:14,370
You.

765
00:36:14,400 --> 00:36:16,920
You go sit in the front courtyard, okay?

766
00:36:17,000 --> 00:36:19,070
The two of you being all
polite back and forth

767
00:36:19,070 --> 00:36:19,950
is exhausting.

768
00:36:20,300 --> 00:36:21,770
The bridal procession hasn't arrived yet.

769
00:36:21,770 --> 00:36:23,900
Let me keep you company a while longer.

770
00:36:24,480 --> 00:36:26,080
How come it's still not here?

771
00:36:26,400 --> 00:36:28,010
The auspicious time has passed, hasn't it?

772
00:36:28,010 --> 00:36:29,410
I feel uneasy.

773
00:36:29,440 --> 00:36:31,210
Go check outside again.

774
00:36:32,950 --> 00:36:35,010
Go and check.

775
00:36:37,200 --> 00:36:38,680
Yes, Great Aunt.

776
00:36:46,720 --> 00:36:47,430
Wan,

777
00:36:48,000 --> 00:36:48,600
come here.

778
00:36:50,670 --> 00:36:51,460
Sit down.

779
00:36:54,760 --> 00:36:56,230
You're such

780
00:36:56,550 --> 00:36:57,610
a straightforward

781
00:36:57,990 --> 00:36:59,260
girl,

782
00:36:59,590 --> 00:37:01,950
so why do you overthink everything?

783
00:37:02,350 --> 00:37:03,880
How did you figure that out?

784
00:37:03,950 --> 00:37:05,880
Well, I've lived for so many years.

785
00:37:05,910 --> 00:37:07,560
If I still couldn't read people,

786
00:37:07,560 --> 00:37:09,690
all those years would've been wasted.

787
00:37:10,420 --> 00:37:11,310
Actually,

788
00:37:11,340 --> 00:37:13,710
I've already found out

789
00:37:14,060 --> 00:37:15,650
all about the kind of life
you’ve been living

790
00:37:15,650 --> 00:37:17,810
in the Qin family by the time
I came looking for you.

791
00:37:17,810 --> 00:37:18,810
No wonder

792
00:37:18,830 --> 00:37:22,100
you're so cautious, afraid to
make even the slightest misstep.

793
00:37:22,100 --> 00:37:25,030
Luckily, fate brought us together.

794
00:37:25,260 --> 00:37:26,490
From now on,

795
00:37:27,270 --> 00:37:28,670
I'll try my best

796
00:37:28,690 --> 00:37:29,860
to protect you,

797
00:37:31,210 --> 00:37:32,110
so you'll never...

798
00:37:32,110 --> 00:37:32,800
Look,

799
00:37:32,820 --> 00:37:35,690
you're making yourself look
like a little old lady.

800
00:37:36,640 --> 00:37:38,210
Be happy.

801
00:37:38,280 --> 00:37:39,110
Smile.

802
00:37:39,510 --> 00:37:41,040
Thank you, Grand Princess.

803
00:37:41,310 --> 00:37:42,750
Hearing your words,

804
00:37:42,780 --> 00:37:44,740
all the grievances in my heart

805
00:37:44,760 --> 00:37:46,290
have completely vanished.

806
00:37:48,020 --> 00:37:51,740
Marquis of Anyang's Mansion

807
00:38:09,220 --> 00:38:10,010
Father,

808
00:38:09,870 --> 00:38:13,020
[Yue Jia, Marquis of Anyang's Heir]

809
00:38:10,590 --> 00:38:12,180
I was sent to escort the bride

810
00:38:12,180 --> 00:38:14,040
and have safely brought her back.

811
00:38:14,680 --> 00:38:15,910
I, Wei Yanzhi,

812
00:38:15,930 --> 00:38:18,180
under orders from the Duke of Song,

813
00:38:16,680 --> 00:38:19,140
[Wei Yanzhi]

814
00:38:18,550 --> 00:38:20,000
have delivered the bride without incident.

815
00:38:20,000 --> 00:38:21,480
Yanzhi, you've endured a long journey.

816
00:38:21,480 --> 00:38:22,670
Thank you for your efforts.

817
00:38:22,670 --> 00:38:23,400
Jia,

818
00:38:23,880 --> 00:38:25,210
you've worked hard too.

819
00:38:26,840 --> 00:38:29,380
The bride has arrived, and
the auspicious hour is here.

820
00:38:29,380 --> 00:38:32,700
Young Master, please kick the sedan door.

